TI  - Toward Interpretable Machine Learning: Constructing Polynomial Models Based on&nbsp;Feature Interaction Trees - Advances in Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining: 27th Pacific-Asia Conference on Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining, PAKDD 2023, Osaka, Japan, May 25–28, 2023, Proceedings, Part II
